install the addon ImportExportTools

to install go to

Open Thunderbird

go to Tools -> Addons

select Extension

search  ImportExportTools

install and restart Thunderbird

now to import MBOX file:

Tools—>ImportExportTools—>Import mbox file

select the MBOX to be imported

remember to select on Thunderbird  a folder like 'Local folder'
otherwise you will get an error

MBOX is a sort of text file half encrypted
